{"tid":1620332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯民意調查:逾七成香港市民撐設「禁蒙面法」","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:14:26.000Z","uid":297241,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":14,"remark":"已收到會員反映本主題內容為2016年2月26日的新聞，請各位會員留意。","replies":[{"pid":"1750cd872c4b73d4121298f64607a303a4acd00d","tid":1620332,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"逾七成香港市民撐設「禁蒙面法」<br />\n<br />\n在旺角暴亂事件中，一批戴口罩或蒙面的暴徒肆意擲磚、縱火、毀壞公物，造成逾120名警員及市民受傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯日前就禁止蒙面法進行民意調查，結果顯示逾七成受訪市民表示支持制訂禁止蒙面法</span>，並建議特區政府應立法禁止示威和集會者以任何方式遮蓋面部。<span style=\"color: red;\">負責是次調查的民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆</span>表示，正就制定蒙面法草擬建議書，並於稍後會約見保安局局長。"},{"pid":"aeb46646d5c510e7ae67af2842c4821a16ac0eab","tid":1620332,"uid":47674,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係超過十成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73dc45c2322e12d3ef1154ded66dbb6a7fc9b64","tid":1620332,"uid":143230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"民建聯招牌跌倒左未？"},{"pid":"67dcb56c28e69df11b2b82bd3e1a7c1fc7825978","tid":1620332,"uid":245441,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"用自己張contact 都得七成？"},{"pid":"9c38022e8c9fa8703fee02c9573e7fe710e949e2","tid":1620332,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d73dc45c2322e12d3ef1154ded66dbb6a7fc9b64","tid":1620332,"uid":143230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"民建聯招牌跌倒左未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"we will see tonight"},{"pid":"4a3e2779a4374e3640e8954390d0e08502c63df3","tid":1620332,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"大家睇識到保皇狗幾仆街未？<br />\n邊個再幫佢地轉移視線<br />\n就一定係打手"},{"pid":"c647ca2e95c6cd0a490f517dba2168c837f9c258","tid":1620332,"uid":200973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"2016年2月26日新聞<br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"bc2432cc188b371e520cf3f9f74dee91b9c25b9a","tid":1620332,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共匪 重奪香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"a28a748d6aeb5f4c4719353885ce886b151f54e9","tid":1620332,"uid":329297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"好 今晚畀你睇下7成市民嘅意願"},{"pid":"02a922c85eeb65b61321bb231815da68efae3888","tid":1620332,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"今晚支線任務：民建聯所有辦事處<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7570eee2bdc0efd9bcd7c2117c2f8da322205665","tid":1620332,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"12成同意，計埋深圳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb211d5a8c745c9610e8c7bb42d7dbf38fb649a4","tid":1620332,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67dcb56c28e69df11b2b82bd3e1a7c1fc7825978","tid":1620332,"uid":245441,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"用自己張contact 都得七成？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"逾七成認同礙警搜證執法<br />\n<br />\n民建聯於本月19日至24日，用電話隨機訪問了731名市民，並於26日公佈調查結果。結果顯示，68.4%受訪者認同，示威者在戴上面具後，由於不怕被人認出，心態上較少顧忌，因而較易作出較激進或暴力的行為;75.3%對示威集會上出現一大班人戴上面具感到「危險」;74.6%則認同，示威者戴上面具會影響警方搜證及執法的工作。"},{"pid":"d6cd832665bd703f8fa08751793d761117015cd3","tid":1620332,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e1ffb10e67b7375761ebf8728a4f108f913ba7","tid":1620332,"uid":237625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"d171c5fbed153f911e1fbf575f0dfa6ed7e4aab0","tid":1620332,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2769316b36bf6f55c058952292b6ae6250f3252c","tid":1620332,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb76af58b8c3d5452e2bbf1d1a4c0599715333b","tid":1620332,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f051b56246f049c0b71cfaabb4fea5c5eb872dd","tid":1620332,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb76af58b8c3d5452e2bbf1d1a4c0599715333b","tid":1620332,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:14:26.000Z","msg":"不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}